===Noun===
'''dweeb'''
# ''(North American slang)'' A boring, studious, or socially inept person.
# 1980's American slang acronym: Dim-Witted Eastern-Educated Boor; being derived 
# from the social differences and attitudes on the West Coast vs. the East Coast.
#Loser
# Often said to describe the typical Ivy-league grads from Harvard, Yale, etc.